      .idx-content-video
        .idx-header-msite
          h1 Training
          p Welcome to our workshop. Here you can watch our short video tutorials and learn how easy it is to get your real estate website up and running!

        .idx-body-video
          article
            h2.idx-icon-rocket Your Control Panel
            p Mission Control is where you can control some of the most important features on your site. Check your leads, manage your account settings, modify your filters, and more. From here you can add content or scoot over to your WordPress dashboard to do things like make design changes or download plugins. And if you need help, you can contact support from here, too.
            ul
              li Manage all of your leads
              li Control your main account settings
              li Configure your IDX settings
              li Control your exclusive and sold inventory
              li Create and manage all of your filters
              li Manage favorite condo buildings
          img(src="../images/min-admin.png")

        .idx-video-list
          ul
            li
              .idx-video-description
                h2 My Leads
                p Track your customers’ activity in real time. You’ll see what properties they searched for and which properties they saved in their favorites.
              .idx-video-content
                a(href="javascript:void(0)", data-video="https://www.youtube.com/embed/r2OT2hpebeI?rel=0&amp;controls=0&amp;showinfo=0").idx-open-video
                  img(src="../images/vd1.jpg")
                  span.idx-video-icon
            li
              .idx-video-description
                h2 My Account
                p Manage all aspects of your account. Update your MLS settings, view and manage your billing preferences and view your registration keys.
              .idx-video-content
                a(href="javascript:void(0)", data-video="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R-JTZ9JsxLg").idx-open-video
                  img(src="../images/vd2.jpg")
                  span.idx-video-icon
            li
              .idx-video-description
                h2 IDX Settings
                p Control which type of properties you want to be displayed on your website, which cities and what price ranges you want to appear.
              .idx-video-content
                a(href="javascript:void(0)", data-video="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R-JTZ9JsxLg").idx-open-video
                  img(src="../images/vd3.jpg")
                  span.idx-video-icon
            li
              .idx-video-description
                h2 My Listings
                p Set your exclusive listings and control how you want them to be displayed. You can also manage your sold properties.
              .idx-video-content
                a(href="javascript:void(0)", data-video="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R-JTZ9JsxLg").idx-open-video
                  img(src="../images/vd4.jpg")
                  span.idx-video-icon
            li
              .idx-video-description
                h2 Filters
                p Build the custom pages for your site. Create filters for neighborhoods, communities, buildings, and more.
              .idx-video-content
                a(href="javascript:void(0)", data-video="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R-JTZ9JsxLg").idx-open-video
                  img(src="../images/vd5.jpg")
                  span.idx-video-icon
            li
              .idx-video-description
                h2 Buildings
                p Manage and control your favorite condo buildings. Add the buildings you want to display and update any information you want.
              .idx-video-content
                a(href="javascript:void(0)", data-video="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R-JTZ9JsxLg").idx-open-video
